msgstr "Create new instance"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:37
msgid "Basic Information"
msgstr "Basic information"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:39
msgid "**Name** : ``oracle-private``"
msgstr "**Name** : ``oracle-private``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:40
msgid "**Image**: *Canonical Ubuntu 24.04 Minimal*"
msgstr "**Image**: *Canonical Ubuntu 24.04 Minimal*"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:41
msgid "**Shape**: VM.Standard.A1.Flex (OCPU = 1, Memory = 1 GB)"
msgstr "**Shape**: VM.Standard.A1.Flex (OCPU = 1, Memory = 1 GB)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:42
msgid "**Always Free–eligible** という表記があることを確認"
msgstr "Make sure it says **Always Free–eligible**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:45
msgid "Networking & SSH"
msgstr "Networking & SSH"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:47
msgid "*Add SSH keys* で **Generate SSH key pair** を選択"
msgstr "*Add SSH keys* and select **Generate SSH key pair**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:48
#, python-brace-format
msgid "ローカルに ``ssh-key-{日付}.key`` (秘密鍵) と ``ssh-key-{日付}.key.pub`` (公開鍵) を保存"
msgstr ""
"Save ``ssh-key-{date}.key`` (private key) and ``ssh-key-{date}.key.pub`` "
"(public key) locally"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:49
#, python-brace-format
msgid ".ssh フォルダに ``ssh-key-{日付}.key`` を移動し、パーミッションを変更"
msgstr "Move ``ssh-key-{date}.key`` to .ssh folder and change permissions"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:53
msgid "鍵ファイルは後でダウンロードできないので忘れずに保存します。"
msgstr "Remember to save the key file as you cannot download it later."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:56
msgid "パブリック IP の確認"
msgstr "Verify your public IP"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:58
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"インスタンス作成完了後、*Instance Details* 画面に表示される **Public IP** を控えます（以下 ``{ip}`` "
"で表記）。"
msgstr ""
"After the instance creation is complete, record the **Public IP** displayed "
"on the *Instance Details* screen (hereinafter expressed as ``{ip}``)."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:61
msgid "Windows からの SSH 接続"
msgstr "SSH connection from Windows"

