msgstr "If you get a permission error"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:74
msgid "秘密鍵の属性を ``600`` に変更すると解消できます。"
msgstr ""
"This can be resolved by changing the private key attribute to ``600``."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:81
msgid "接続確認"
msgstr "Connection confirmation"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:83
msgid "ログイン後に ``uname -a`` が返れば接続成功です。"
msgstr ""
"If ``uname -a`` is returned after logging in, the connection is successful."

