msgid "まとめ"
msgstr "summary"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:88
msgid "Oracle Cloud **Always Free** を使えば 10 分ほどでパーソナル Linux サーバを構築できる"
msgstr ""
"Build a personal Linux server in 10 minutes with Oracle Cloud **Always "
"Free**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:89
msgid "SSH 鍵のパーミッション設定に注意"
msgstr "Be careful about SSH key permission settings"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-04-30-oracle-always-free.rst:90
